        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"مَنْ قَالَ عَلَيَّ مَا لَمْ أَقُلْ فَلْيَتَبَوَّأْ مَقْعَدَهُ مِنَ اَلنَّارِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4942 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Whoever attributes to Me (sw) something I did not say, let him prepare his seat in the Fire.\""
        ]
